data.description: Assumable Loan at 2.75% available with this beautiful Ptarmigan home on the 12th fairway!  Pre-inspected and move in ready, make this home your holiday gift! Pride of ownership radiates from the home as you view the beautiful lawn and entry way. The sound of a running brook welcomes you.  4,615 sq ft home with 3 car attached garage, lush landscaping and beautiful entryway only gets better once inside! As you enter the home, light spills through from abundant soaring windows, speckled as it shines through the trees.   The maple hardwood floors create a warm feeling to the open floor plan.  The updated kitchen, with quartz counter tops, and large center island, looks out to the fireplaced living room, and to the landscaped backyard with hardscaped features, firepit, pergola, and hot tub.  A small waterfall bathes the yard in the tranquil sound of running water.  Separate main floor office and a mud room (which could convert back to main floor laundry) off the garage make the home functional as well as beautiful.   Upstairs is the primary suite with remodeled 5 piece bath, tile and maple hardwood floors.   Two more bedrooms share a Jack and Jill bath, and a third bedroom has a private full bath.   Guests staying for a visit?  They can venture downstairs to the finished basement with bedroom, full bath, and family room. Select a bottle of wine from the wine room to enjoy! Pre-Inspected for your convenience, with newer utilities and appliances.  Do not miss this wonderful home.   It is waiting for you to make it your own!
